 outstanding and impressive guardian dog.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n30\n\ndefault\n\nGallery\n\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"2989,2951,2959,77,78,2958\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nbounceIn\n\nHeading\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #fff;\">Want organic foods from our farm?</h3>\r\n[divider height=\"15\"]\r\n[button title=\"Buy Organic\" link=\"http://wangsfarm/themarket/\" color=\"#00c579\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" large=\"1\"]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nbounceIn\n\n'),(266,86,'_dp_original','20'),(267,86,'_edit_lock','1496362109:1'),(268,86,'_edit_last','1'),(269,86,'slide_template','default'),(270,86,'_wpb_vc_js_status','false'),(284,90,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(285,90,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(286,90,'_wp_page_template','default'),(287,90,'mfn-post-hide-content','0'),(288,90,'mfn-post-custom-layout','0'),(289,90,'mfn-post-slider','0'),(290,90,'mfn-post-slider-layer','2'),(291,90,'mfn-post-menu','0'),(292,90,'mfn-post-one-page','0'),(293,90,'mfn-post-hide-title','0'),(294,90,'mfn-post-remove-padding','0'),(295,90,'mfn-page-items',''),(296,90,'mfn-page-items-seo','30\n\ndefault\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h5>Dogs are our best friends</h5>\r\n<p class=\"big\">We are family run farm located at tweed, north of Belleville, Ontario. Our current working line German Shepherds have excellent temperaments, great drive, pronounced retrieval instincts, vibrant markings and intelligence that is true to the German Shepherd</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<h5>GSD Puppies are the most adorable creature in the world</h5>\r\n<p class=\"big\">Our German Shepherd pups have plenty of space to run and play and are exercised daily, as well as being socialized with our other animals, and children. They have plenty of fun swimming in our pond, chasing wild animals and harmonizing with the coyotes.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nGallery\n\n[gallery link=\"file\" id