ultry always find unusual places to lay their eggs.</p>\r\n<p class=\"big\">We are currently trying to raise fertilized chicken eggs so we can have more chicken and eggs in order to grow our chicken farm. Once h successful, we will do the same with our ducks.</p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n<img src=\"http://wangsfarm.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/IMG_5004.jpg\" alt=\"IMG_5004\"/>\n\n30\n\ndefault\n\n<img src=\"http://wangsfarm.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/findegg.jpeg\" alt=\"findegg\"/>\n\n250\n\n250\n\n<img src=\"http://wangsfarm.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/eggs.jpg\" alt=\"eggs\"/>\n\nHeading + desc\n\n<p class=\"big\">We have all type of poultry, chicken, rooster, duck, turkey and goose</p>\r\n<p class=\"big\">Our poultry are free range, organic, and non-GMO. Studies show that eggs and meat from free-range poultry are healthier for us. There are higher nutrient content in the eggs. Free-range chickens have 21% less total fat, 30% less saturated fat and 28% fewer calories than their factory-farmed counterparts. </p>\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n30\n\ndefault\n\nGallery\n\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"3064,3073,3074,3065,3067,3070,3086,3084,3087\"]\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\nbounceIn\n\nHeading\n\n<h3 style=\"color: #fff;\">Want organic foods from our farm?</h3>\r\n[divider height=\"15\"]\r\n[button title=\"Buy Organic\" link=\"http://wangsfarm.com/themarket/\" color=\"#00c579\" font_color=\"#ffffff\" large=\"1\"]\n\ncenter\n\nno-repeat;center top;;\n\nauto\n\n'),(2967,2967,'slide_template','default'),(2968,2967,'_wpb_vc_js_status','false'),(2969,2967,'_dp_original','90'),(2970,2967,'_edit_lock','1497739604:1'),(2971,2967,'_edit_last','1'),(2972,2971,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(2973,2971,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(2974,2971,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(2975,2971,'_vc_post_settings','a:1:{s:10:\"vc_grid_id\";a:0:{}}'),(2976,2971,'_wp_page_templat